Line1.BD31C: Sanctuary was meant as an escape from the Eternal Conflict...and yet here we are...again...
Line11.BD31C: You chose tyranny when offered freedom. A poor legacy for my gift.
Line13.BD31C: Without me...you would have no...victory. And its cost will be more...than you can pay.
Line7.BD31C: I gave you free will...and you’ve squandered it...wasting it on a crusade you don’t understand...
